@startuml
title Live UiPlugin Runtime Product Sequence

actor Human
actor Agent
participant "ui_counter_runtime" as AppBin
participant "App" as App
participant "UiPlugin" as Ui
participant "CounterPlugin" as CounterPlugin
participant "CounterScreen" as Screen
participant "ui_definition / ui_program" as Program
participant "ui_hosts" as Host
participant "Trace / History" as Trace
participant "ui_evaluator / runtime_view" as Eval
participant "Render Publisher" as Publisher
participant "RenderPlugin" as Render
participant "Console / JSONL" as Console

AppBin -> App: App::new().add_plugins((RenderPlugin, UiPlugin, CounterPlugin))
CounterPlugin -> App: app.mount_ui(CounterScreen)
App -> Ui: record mount request
Ui -> Screen: IntoUi
Screen -> Program: source + routes + capability facts
Ui -> Trace: UiSourceLowered / UiProgramFormed

alt human pointer or keyboard input
  Human -> Ui: input event from window runtime
else agent script
  Agent -> Ui: semantic action or scripted pointer event
end

Ui -> Host: route + capability + payload validation
Host -> Trace: UiCapabilityChecked
alt accepted
  Host -> CounterPlugin: mutate Counter resource
  Host -> Trace: UiHostMutationApplied
else rejected
  Host -> Trace: UiHostMutationRejected
end

Ui -> Eval: evaluate source/program/session/host snapshot
Eval -> Trace: UiRuntimeEvaluated
Eval -> Publisher: frame payload + report facts
Publisher -> Trace: UiFramePublished
Publisher -> Render: producer surface-frame submission
Render -> Trace: UiFramePresented
Trace -> Console: bounded history + JSONL export
Render -> Human: visible updated UI
Agent -> Console: read JSONL / assert state and frame facts

@enduml
